fl-draft-sites/ |archive-date=2015-09-05 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n==Player selections==\n{|\n|-\n|style=\"background-color:#CCFFCC; border:1px solid #aaaaaa; width:2em;\"|\n|= [[Pro Football Hall of Fame|Hall of Fame]]r\n|}\n\n===Round one===\n<!-- The Team names, player positions, and college names should only be linked the first time they appear in the entire page -->\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable sortable\" style=\"width: 100%\"\n|-\n!style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\" width=7%|Pick # !!width=40% style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\"|NFL Team !!width=20% style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\"|Player !!width=13% style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\"|Position !!style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\"|College\n|-\n|align=center|1||[[History of the Arizona Cardinals#Chicago years (1898\u20131959)|Chicago Cardinals]]||[[George Cafego]]||[[Running back|Tailback]]||[[University of Tennessee|Tennessee]]\n|-\n|align=center|2||[[Philadelphia Eagles]]||bgcolor=\"#CCFFCC\"|[[George McAfee]]||[[Quarterback]]||[[Duke University|Duke]]\n|-\n|align=center|3||[[Pittsburgh Steelers]]||[[Kay Eakin]]||Halfback||[[University of Arkansas|Arkansas]]\n|-\n|align=center|4||[[Brooklyn Dodgers (NFL)|Brooklyn Dodgers]]||[[Banks McFadden]]||Halfback||[[Clemson University|Clemson]]\n|-\n|align=center|5||[[Cleveland Rams]]||[[Olie Cordill]]||Halfback||[[Rice University|Rice]]\n|-\n|align=center|6||[[Detroit Lions]]||Doyle Nave||Quarterback||[[University of Southern California|USC]]\n|-\n|align=center|7||[[Chicago Bears]]||bgcolor=\"#CCFFCC\"|[[Bulldog Turner|Clyde \"Bulldog\" Turner]]||[[Center (American football)|Center]]||[[Hardin\u2013Simmons University|Hardin\u2013Simmons]]\n|-\n|align=center|8||[[Washington Redskins]]||Ed Boell||Quarterback||[[New York University|NYU]]\n|-\n|align=center|9||[[Green Bay Packers]]||[[Hal Van Every]]||Halfback||[[University of Minnesota|Minnesota]]\n|-\n|align=center|10||[[New York Giants]]||[[Grenny Lansdell]]||Quarterback||USC\n|}\n\n===Round two===\n<!-- The Team names, player positions, an