ibar]]||Guard||Duke\n|-\n|align=center|167||Chicago Bears||Ralph Schlosser||Center||Gonzaga\n|-\n|align=center|168||Washington Redskins||Jay Graybeal||Back||Oregon\n|-\n|align=center|169||Green Bay Packers||[[Jim Gillette (American football)|Jim Gillette]]||Back||Virginia\n|-\n|align=center|170||New York Giants||[[Bill Edwards (offensive lineman)|Bill \"Monk\" Edwards]]||Tackle||Baylor\n|}\n\n===Round nineteen===\n<!-- The Team names, player positions, and college names should only be linked the first time they appear in the entire page -->\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable sortable\" style=\"width: 100%\"\n|-\n!style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\" width=7%|Pick # !!width=40% style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\"|NFL Team !!width=20% style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\"|Player !!width=13% style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\"|Position !!style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\"|College\n|-\n|align=center|171||Chicago Cardinals||Russ Buckley||Back||Gustavus Adolphus\n|-\n|align=center|172||Philadelphia Eagles||Bill Schneller||Back||Mississippi\n|-\n|align=center|173||Pittsburgh Steelers||Thad Harvey||Tackle||Notre Dame\n|-\n|align=center|174||Brooklyn Dodgers||Steve Hydock||End||Albright\n|-\n|align=center|175||Cleveland Rams||[[Dante Magnani]]||Back||St. Mary's (CA)\n|-\n|align=center|176||Detroit Lions||Herb McCarthy||Back||Denver\n|-\n|align=center|177||Chicago Bears||John Popov||Back||Cincinnati\n|-\n|align=center|178||Washington Redskins||Charley Slagle||Back||North Carolina\n|-\n|align=center|179||Green Bay Packers||[[Al Matuza]]||Center||Georgetown\n|-\n|align=center|180||New York Giants||Cecil Walden||Guard||Oregon\n|}\n\n===Round twenty===\n<!-- The Team names, player positions, and college names should only be linked the first time they appear in the entire page -->\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable sortable\" style=\"width: 100%\"\n|-\n!style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\" width=7%|Pick # !!width=40% style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\"|NFL Team !!width=20% style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\"|Player !!width=13% style=\"backg