ge=University of Utah | collegeteam=Utah Utes | collegelink=Utah | probowl=no | note= | cfb page exists=yes}}\n\n{{NFLDraft-row| draftyear=1940 | undrafted=yes | round= | picknum= | team=Green Bay Packers | first=Ray | last=Riddick | dab= | position=End | collegeyear=1939 | college=Fordham University | collegeteam=Fordham Rams | collegelink=Fordham | probowl=no | note= | cfb page exists=yes}}\n\n{{NFLDraft-row| draftyear=1940 | undrafted=yes | round= | picknum= | team=New York Giants | first=Jack | last=Hinkle | dab= | position=Running back | collegeyear=1939 | college=Syracuse University | collegeteam=Syracuse Orangemen | collegelink=Syracuse | probowl=no | note= | cfb page exists=yes}}\n\n{{NFLDraft-row| draftyear=1940 | undrafted=yes | round= | picknum= | team=Pittsburgh Steelers | first=Tommy | last=Thompson | dab=Tommy Thompson (quarterback) | position=Quarterback | collegeyear=1939 | college=University of Tulsa | collegeteam=Tulsa Golden Hurricane | collegelink=Tulsa | probowl=yes | note= | cfb page exists=yes}}\n\n{{NFLDraft-row| draftyear=1940 | undrafted=yes | round= | picknum= | team=Washington Redskins | first=Ray | last=Hare |  position=Running Back | collegeyear=1939 | college=Gonzaga University | collegeteam=Gonzaga Bulldogs | collegelink=Gonzaga | probowl=yes | note= | cfb page exists=yes}}\n\n{{NFLDraft-footer}}\n\n==References==\n<references/>\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.nfl.com/draft/history/fulldraft?season=1940 NFL.com&nbsp;\u2013 1940 Draft]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20080327013702/http://www.databasefootball.com/draft/draftyear.htm?yr=1940&lg=NFL databaseFootball.com&nbsp;\u2013 1940 Draft]\n* [http://www.profootballhof.com/history/general/draft/1940.jsp Pro Football Hall of Fame]\n\n{{NFL drafts}}\n{{1940 NFL season by team}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:1940 Nfl Draft}}\n[[Category:National Football League Draft|1940]]\n[[Category:1940 National Football League season|Draft]]\n[[Category:1939 in sports in Wisconsin|NFL draft]]\n", "text_old