ith (American football)|Harry Smith]]||Guard||USC\n|-\n|align=center|37||Chicago Bears||[[Ed Kolman]]||Tackle||Temple\n|-\n|align=center|38||Washington Redskins||Bill Kirchem||Tackle||Tulane\n|-\n|align=center|39||Green Bay Packers||Esco Sarkkinen||End||Ohio State\n|-\n|align=center|40||New York Giants||Carl Tomasello||End||Scranton\n|}\n\n===Round six===\n<!-- The Team names, player positions, and college names should only be linked the first time they appear in the entire page -->\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable sortable\" style=\"width: 100%\"\n|-\n!style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\" width=7%|Pick # !!width=40% style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\"|NFL Team !!width=20% style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\"|Player !!width=13% style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\"|Position !!style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\"|College\n|-\n|align=center|41||Chicago Cardinals||Vic Reginato||End||Oregon\n|-\n|align=center|42||Pittsburgh Steelers||[[Frank Bykowski]]||Guard||Purdue\n|-\n|align=center|43||Philadelphia Eagles||Saul Singer||Tackle||Arkansas\n|-\n|align=center|44||Brooklyn Dodgers||Jack Murray||Center||Wisconsin\n|-\n|align=center|45||Cleveland Rams||Ken Heineman||Back||Texas-El Paso\n|-\n|align=center|46||Detroit Lions||Jim Rike||Center||Tennessee\n|-\n|align=center|47||Chicago Bears||[[John Woudenberg]]||Tackle||Denver\n|-\n|align=center|48||Washington Redskins||Joe Boyd||Tackle||Texas A&M\n|-\n|align=center|49||Green Bay Packers||[[Dick Cassiano]]||Back||Pittsburgh\n|-\n|align=center|50||New York Giants||Lou Smith||Back||California\n|}\n\n===Round seven===\n<!-- The Team names, player positions, and college names should only be linked the first time they appear in the entire page -->\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable sortable\" style=\"width: 100%\"\n|-\n!style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\" width=7%|Pick # !!width=40% style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\"|NFL Team !!width=20% style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\"|Player !!width=13% style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\"|Position !!style=\"background:#A8BDEC;\"|College\n|-\n|align=center|51|